title: Is It Better To Be Famous or Impactful?, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO231
itunes:title: Is It Better To Be Famous or Impactful?, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO231
description: There's a question that I think – if you answer it rightly – will get you straight on what you’re doing with your business, your brand….even your whole life. If you answer this question correctly, you’re going to have a sense of strength and purpose that other people dream about. And you’re going to feel good about yourself.  So here’s the question: is it better to be famous or impactful? That's what I talk through on today's episode.  [Visit Andy's website](www.andyfrisella.com)
